      "side": 1,
      "message": "Nodir: Sorry, you may have to rephrase that. That link contains an explicit recommendation for a parent field, but your phrasing implies that the API guidelines _don\u0027t_ explicitly recommend that.\n\n\u003e the format \"invocations/{INVOCATION_ID}/tests/{URL_ESCAPED_TEST_ID}/results/{RESULT_ID}\", wouldn\u0027t that be sufficient?\n\nNo, it would not. Having to parse a complex string is not a good way to retrieve this information either.",
      "parentUuid": "2cb57849_d89d1053",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 128,
        "startChar": 9,
        "endLine": 128,
        "endChar": 22
      },
