      "writtenOn": "2020-10-19T17:19:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "in https://google.aip.dev/122#fields-representing-a-resources-parent, parent field is in the request message, not a resource message. There is no recommendation to have a parent field in the resource message.\n\n\u003e parse a complex a string\n\n  invocation \u003d name.split(\u0027/\u0027)[1]\n\n?",
      "parentUuid": "71a2207f_549fe58f",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 128,
        "startChar": 9,
